**SECTION 2: TRUCK RECEIVING & UNLOADING BAYS**

**2.1 Design Philosophy - No Manual Shoveling**

**CRITICAL REQUIREMENT:** Zero manual shoveling by workers. All material
transfer is mechanized for safety, efficiency, and consistent
throughput.

**Solution:** Elevated tipping ramps with direct gravity discharge into
receiving hoppers with automatic feeders.

**2.2 EFB Unloading Bay #1**

