                   To BC-10 conveyor``
`

**DC Handling Considerations:**

-   **Slurry consistency:** DC is wet paste (75-85% MC), flows more
    easily than EFB - screw feeder better than apron

-   **Odor control:** DC contains residual organics, slight anaerobic
    odor - enclosed transfer, ventilation to biofilter (optional)

-   **Oil content:** DC has 5-15% residual palm oil - all equipment
    304SS or oil-resistant coatings

-   **Settling prevention:** If DC sits \>4 hours in hopper, solids
    settle - agitator (2.2 kW paddle) keeps suspension

**Operator Actions:**

-   Similar to EFB bay, but truck driver must ensure complete dump (DC
    sticks to truck bed) - may require manual scraping or water hose
    rinse

