``│``    ``│``  - KOH + CO``₂`` ``→`` KHCO₃ (potassium bicarbonate)         │        │``
│    │  - Ca(OH)₂ + CO₂ → ``CaCO``₃ + H₂O (limestone)           │        │``
│    │  - pH drops: 10-12 → 8 over 12 hours                 │        │``
│    │  - Slight exotherm: Temp rises 5-10°C                │        │``
