│    │  - Spray 82m³ diluted POME (1:1 water)               │        │``
│    │  - Bobcat turns windrow 2-3 passes                   │        │``
│    │  - POME acidity → pH 7-7.5                           │        │``
│    │                                                       │        │``
│    │  PHASE 2 (12-24 hours): Final cure                    │        │``
│    │  - Continue passive carbonation                       │        │``
│    │  - pH stabilizes at 6.5-8.0                          │        │``
│    │  - Temperature <45°C (check before biology)          │        │``
│    │                                                       │        │``
│    └───────────────────────────``┬``───────────────────────────┘``        ``│``
``│``                                ``│``                                    ``│``
