│  • Fire extinguishers: 20 kg dry powder, 15m spacing                      │``
│  • Eye wash stations: Near PKSA mixer (3 locations)                       │``
│  • Emergency assembly point: 50m south of buildings                       │``
│  • First aid room: 12 m² (adjacent to MCC room)                           │``
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘``
`

**5.2 Building Heights & Structural Requirements**

**Stage 1 Building (30m × 15m × 8m H):**

-   **Clear height:** 8m allows elevated conveyors at 5m + 3m clearance
    above for crane hook access, lighting, ventilation

-   **Structure:** Pre-engineered steel building (PEB) with insulated
    metal cladding (roof + walls)

-   **Foundation:** Isolated footings for steel columns (1.5m × 1.5m ×
    2m deep), grade beam perimeter

-   **Floor:** Reinforced concrete slab 150mm thick, 25 MPa compressive,
    mesh reinforcement (150mm grid)

-   **Crane:** Optional 2-ton⁂

